&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.zhouxiaozhao.cn/2021/01/14/2021-01-14RNAseq(22)/&#34;&gt;Functional Annotation of Assembled Transcripts Using Trinotate&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
